--- !u!114 &1696623480
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1696623479}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f5751978dfa734eea81e24a0dec56305, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CutscenePlayer
  playOnStart: 0
  startSlides:
  - layout: 0
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: 'It is a cold winter night, and the sky is pitch-black. A faint glow spills
      from the coffee shop windows onto the empty city streets.


      Inside, Dahlia
      moves quietly. A barista by day, she wipes down the last of the tables and
      sweeps the floor.'
    rollingText: 1
    highlights:
    - word: Dahlia
      color: {r: 0.4627451, g: 0.6117647, b: 0.33333334, a: 0}
    sounds: []
  - layout: 0
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: 'But as the hour grows late, the lights dim and so Dahlia fades with them,
      slipping into the darkness and leaving the coffee shop behind.


      The
      distant hum of industry and the occasional hiss of steam can be heard howling
      through the night.


      In her place, emerges an experienced assassin. Tonight,
      Hemlock roams the streets of old London, hunting for her prey.'
    rollingText: 1
    highlights:
    - word: Hemlock
      color: {r: 0.4627451, g: 0.6117647, b: 0.33333334, a: 0}
    sounds: []
  slides:
  - layout: 0
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: 
    rollingText: 0
    highlights:
    - word: Hemlock
      color: {r: 0.4627451, g: 0.6117647, b: 0.33333334, a: 0}
    - word: Alfonso
      color: {r: 0.9843137, g: 0.45490196, b: 0.45490196, a: 0}
    sounds:
    - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 99f760439c37d4e8d8bce89a54cd784f, type: 3}
      offset: 1
    - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2845a9f7c9e874709b61d3dcb1191e57, type: 3}
      offset: 1.5
    - clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4982ede5934244f7db5a193fb4985e64, type: 3}
      offset: 1.6
  - layout: 1
    image: {fileID: 4345347192318643893, guid: 6f16acb8e07e14dc6a353547e70aa5a3, type: 3}
    text: "The cold steel of Hemlock\u2019s blade pierces an unknowing investigators
      flesh."
    rollingText: 1
    highlights:
    - word: Hemlock
      color: {r: 0.4627451, g: 0.6117647, b: 0.33333334, a: 0}
    sounds: []
  - layout: 1
    image: {fileID: 4345347192318643893, guid: 6f16acb8e07e14dc6a353547e70aa5a3, type: 3}
    text: A victim is claimed in the dead of night, without a witness in sight.
    rollingText: 1
    highlights: []
    sounds: []
  - layout: 0
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Leaving the site of the scene, she vanishes swiftly through the narrow
      alley roads.\n\nThrough the thick fog, she arrives at the iron gate of a grand
      mansion, the guards let Hemlock in as she is escorted to Alfonso\u2019s office."
    rollingText: 1
    highlights:
    - word: Hemlock
      color: {r: 0.4627451, g: 0.6117647, b: 0.33333334, a: 0}
    - word: Alfonso
      color: {r: 0.9843137, g: 0.45490196, b: 0.45490196, a: 0}
    sounds: []
  textOnlyLayout: {fileID: 1246845054}
  textOnlyDialogue: {fileID: 1560838455}
  textOnlyProceed: {fileID: 0}
  textWithImageLayout: {fileID: 525054737}
  displayImage: {fileID: 620895664}
  textWithImageDialogue: {fileID: 146843935}
  textWithImageProceed: {fileID: 0}
  sfxSource: {fileID: 1696623486}
  fadeInDuration: 0.5
  fadeOutDuration: 0.5
  advanceKey: 19
  charDelay: 0.04
  flagOnComplete: 
  targetScene: Scene2-Base
  targetSpawnPointName: Scene2-spawn
  spawnDirection: 4
